reviewText:
Christina Aguilera. Yum. I give her a shooting gallery-sized 11. Coney Island. Looky here, son. You'd better start using phantom bullets.

This DVD proves she is a shooting gallery-sized 11.

The title on Amazon is: "Christina Aguilera: More Than a Woman by Christina Aguilera".  Note the phrase 'by Christine Aguilera'.  On the back of the DVD is the statement:  THIS DVD IS NOT AUTHORISED BY CHRISTINA AGUILERA, HER MANAGEMENT OR RECORD LABEL.  It contains no music from Christina Aguilera.  Amazon should be ashamed for offering this piece of junk -- especially for $17.99.
